### 1. Add new task
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test DB",
  "completed": false
}

###

### 2. Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks

###

### 3. Get task by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks/1

###

### 4. Update task
PUT http://localhost:8080/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn Spring Boot Deeply",
  "completed": true
}

###

### 5. Delete task
DELETE http://localhost:8080/tasks/1

###

### 6. Verify deletion
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks/1

### 7. Get non-existing task
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks/999

### 8. Invalid task (empty title)
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "completed": false
}
